T1  - Targeting of food aid in rural Ethiopia: chronic need or inertia?
AU  - Jayne, Thomas S
AU  - Strauss, John
AU  - Yamano, Takashi
AU  - Molla, Daniel
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 68
IS  - 2
SP  - 247
